channel.title: Corrupt-Specz v3
channel.description:
hey well heres the history of Corrupt-Specz iunreal-pkz is the name of that i used to call my server i changed my server name at one point because i wanted new players and i also changed ip first it was called corrupt-specz. then i changed it to Unreal-Pkz which i used 2 years back for my edge pvp source then i currently changed back to Corrupt-Specz. my first ever username was corrupt-claw which you will see on first forums my 2nd was unreal and my last and final username is The Funeral 2nd owner name was Corruption then Reality and is still Reality
well this is Corrupt-Specz v3 this is the same source i used when i ran my server well one of the sources v3 of it and now im releasing it. took away the customs since there where so many complaints.
No more Anoying pvp changer. Pk inside the wild at Mage Bank by pulling lever. Lever actuly works. Changed some shops. Took away customs. Fixed up dds spec
Commands Noclip Uber Yell (donators only) xteleall shop home spec mypos blowjob hail pnpc combat emote auto spawn Info demote givehidden, mod, admin, donator, and owner veng brunes arrows warning staffzone npc bootall kick npcreset mauler ddser zerker inipure pure master tank tele unban banuser ipban mute unmute ipmute copy xteletome xteleto bank pickup Some more i cant think of atm
